Release 1.0 (development)
----------------------------------

.. note::

   This version is the first official release of RAUC hawkBit Updater.

.. rubric:: Enhancements

* Allow following HTTP redirects

.. rubric:: Testing

* Switch from Travis-CI to GitHub actions.
* Add pytest-based testsuite

.. rubric:: Code

* Refactoring

.. rubric:: Documentation

* Add sphinx-based user documentation

.. rubric:: Bug fixes

* Memoryleaks
* Use-after-frees
* Raceconditions
* Fix free storage space calculation overflowing

Release 0.1 (in development)
----------------------------

This is the initial release of RAUC hawkBit Updater.
